  "description": {
    "zh": "我又接了个新活儿，这次是两把狙击步枪，一把 雷明顿M700，一把 T5000M。能帮我一把吗？太好了！\n\n两把枪都需要至少 5 发弹容量和两脚架。M700 需要能打出 1500 米的射程，T5000M 则要能打出 2000 米远，M700 的初速还得超过 900 米/秒，T5000M 要可折叠并带有消音器。搞得定吗？\n\nM700 要求：\n - 重量小于 3.9 公斤\n - 人机功效 51 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 95 %\n - 弹匣容量 5 或更多\n - “射击场”距离 1500米 或更多\n - 膛口初速 达到 900M/s 或更多\n - 任意 脚架\n\nT-5000M 要求：\n - 重量小于 8.0 公斤\n - 人机功效 40 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 95 %\n - 弹匣容量 5 或更多\n - 宽度占用 6格 或更少\n - “射击场”距离 2000米 或更多\n - 任意 脚架\n - 任意 消音器",
    "en": "Hey I got another order, this time I need two sniper rifles. A Remington model 700 and a T5000M. Can you help out a little? Great!\n\nBoth weapons need to hold at least five rounds in the magazine and a bipod, the M700 should be able to take a shot from fifteen-hundred meters and the T5000M should be able to do that from two-thousand meters away. The Remington should have a muzzle velocity of at least nine-hundred meters per second. The T5000 should be foldable and be suppressed. Can you handle that?\n\nM700 Requirements :\n - Weight less than 3.9 KG\n - Ergonomics 51 or higher\n - Durability higher than 95 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 5 or more\n - Sighting Range of 1500 Meters or more\n - Muzzle Velocity of 900 M/s or more\n - A Bipod\n\nT-5000M Requirements :\n - Weight less than 8.0 KG\n - Ergonomics 40 or higher\n - Durability higher than 95 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 5 or more\n - Width of 6 slots or less\n - Sighting Range of 2000 Meters or more\n - A Bipod\n - A Silencer"
  },
